      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54B32 inline-six, delivering 333hp through six individual throttle bodies and a high-revving 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission and a factory variable M differential lock. Recent mechanical stewardship includes a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement, critical for maintaining structural rigidity under high torque loads. The chassis is dialed in with upgraded bushings and adjustable dampers, offering sharp turn-in and exceptional mechanical grip. While showing honest signs of use consistent with its mileage, the engine pulls strong with a linear power band and the iconic rasp of the factory quad-exit exhaust. A mechanically sound, driver-focused example ready for technical backroads.",
